HEADWORD: bootleg
<hw>bootleg</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>distributed or sold illicitly;
especially, imported illegally.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> black-market, contraband, smuggled.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

